@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_cvwiac(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = 0.35
    tmp = (wp.abs((v1 + 0.05 - v2 + 0.45)) + (v0 * wp.exp(tmp + 0.40)))
    v2 = 0.61
    v1 = (((v2 + 0.63 + v0 + 0.86) - (v0 + 0.81 * v1 + 0.68)) / (wp.cos(v0 + 0.84) / 0.11))
    data[tid] = v0
